This test tries to access every port-message location in the ET-SoC1
memory map and the equivalent one in the Erbium memory map. There is
no number of threads expected to be running but the test designer
expects the whole neighborhood to be running so all the possible
combiation of sender hart + destination port are covered

The test expect that all these accesses end up in a access fault
exception since messagess extensions is removed in erbium.